---
import CTAButton from "../ui/CTAButton.astro";
import NavigationHint from "../ui/NavigationHint.astro";
---

<!-- About Section -->
<section
  id="about"
  class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About Tam</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-lg sm:prose-xl prose-invert max-w-none mb-12">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6">
        A special brand of philosophical counseling that honors you as a growing
        being. While therapy addresses how you're faring—your present state,
        symptoms, or wellbeing—our specialty is your growth trajectory through
        conversations about what's truly important to you.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
        I'm not here to give you wise advice or assess how you're doing. As your
        philosophical counselor, I become an ongoing companion in your growth,
        work, and learning—a power listener who takes your mind seriously,
        helping you discover the wisdom and experience you've accumulated but
        haven't yet articulated.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-6">
        Certified by the <a
          href="https://appa.edu/about/"
          class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline">APPA</a
        > (American Philosophical Practitioners Association).
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">
        With a background in software development, we've built custom
        infrastructure to create AI-optimized transcripts, bridging ancient
        wisdom with cutting-edge technology.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="text-2xl font-medium italic border-none">
        "The counselor comes not with advice but with generative questions,<br
        />
        a fortifying curiosity"
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <!-- Let's talk CTA -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <CTAButton variant="secondary" />
    </div>

    <NavigationHint href="#process" text="What to expect" />
  </div>
</section>
